<div class="well col-sm-12 col-md-12 homepage_info">
  <p>The Homosaurus is an international linked data vocabulary of LGBTQ+ terms. Designed to enhance broad subject term vocabularies, the Homosaurus is a robust and cutting-edge thesaurus that advances the discoverability of LGBTQ+ resources and information.</p>

  <p>If you are interested in purchasing some Homosaurus swag, please visit our <%= link_to "online shop", "https://homosaurus.threadless.com" %>. All proceeds are used to support the project or are donated to LGBTQ+ organizations.</p>

  <p>If you are using the Homosaurus, we want to hear from you! Please <%= link_to "contact us", contact_path %> to let us know how you are using this vocabulary and share any feedback you might have. One can also join our Google Group community at: <%= link_to "https://groups.google.com/g/homoitcommunity", "https://groups.google.com/g/homoitcommunity" %></p>
